Package org.universAAL.middleware.interfaces.configuration.configurationDefinitionTypes

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfigurationFile
    A configuration entity that refers to a file.
    ConfigurationParameter
    An Configuration entity that refers to a configuration parameter.
    DescribedEntity
    A DescribedEntity is an Entity that is restricted to certain Scope and has a description.
    DynamicDescribedEntity
    Additonally to DescribedEntities, this interfaced may be added.
    DynamicDescribedEntityListener
    Listener to be called when a DynamicDescribedEntity changes value.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigurationDefinedElsewhere
    Use this implementation when the configuration Entity is described elsewhere.
